beer.beer_description: Glenn's Negroni Pilsner is a wildly ambitious combination of two classic beverages from opposite sides of the drinking experience. Saaz Hops and Pilsner malt provide a clean base beer for freshly pressed bitter orange juice to bring some body and sweetness to the mid palate, whilst a carefully selected blend of herbs and botanicals get to work on the back end. The result is a fresh and dry Pilsner with a delicately herbaceous and bitter finish emulating the modern classic cocktail, the Negroni.
